lead_paragraph: A year after announcing his retirement from full-time golf, Anders Hansen took a share of the lead at the Portugal Masters after going 9-under 62 through the third round on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Hansen Shares Lead of Portugal Masters After 3 Rounds
